305
00:24:30,980 --> 00:24:32,980
You're not going to Canada anymore?

306
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:35,840
Nope.

307
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:37,210
I've made up my mind.

308
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:38,800
I'm going to take you back to China,

309
00:24:38,800 --> 00:24:39,710
to Nanjing.

310
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:40,970
From now on, we'll live together

311
00:24:40,970 --> 00:24:42,250
in that old house,

312
00:24:42,430 --> 00:24:44,360
