be worse than his too?

334
00:26:20,250 --> 00:26:21,550
There won't be a next time.

335
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:23,240
There won't be a next time!

336
00:26:23,910 --> 00:26:25,800
There won't be a next time!

337
00:26:26,120 --> 00:26:26,970
Get lost!

338
00:27:23,430 --> 00:27:24,360
Thank you.

339
00:27:29,430 --> 00:27:30,560
Jin Qiang called.

340
00:27:31,730 --> 00:27:33,660
He said your mom arrived in Manshi.

341
00:27:37,770 --> 00:27:38,970
Let me take you there.

342
00:27:41,110 --> 00:27:41,910
Okay.

343
00:28:34,190 --> 00:28:35,150
Do you...

344
00:28:36,430 --> 00:28:37,800
