345
00:28:39,910 --> 00:28:40,560
No.

346
00:28:44,950 --> 00:28:45,670
Go ahead.

347
00:28:59,630 --> 00:29:00,190
Mu,

348
00:29:00,470 --> 00:29:01,670
actually, your Uncle Chris

349
00:29:01,670 --> 00:29:03,040
cares about you very much.

350
00:29:03,040 --> 00:29:05,770
He's already arranged
a school for you in Canada.

351
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:07,230
You can continue your studies

352
00:29:07,230 --> 00:29:08,600
and further education there.

353
00:29:08,600 --> 00:29:09,600
I won't go.

354
00:29:10,230 --> 00:29:12,290
If not Canada, then where will you go?

355
00:29:13,230 --> 00:29:14,490
I've already decided.

356
00:29:14,600 --> 00:29:16,650
After graduating, I'll stay in China.

357
00:29:16,650 --> 00:29:18,050
I won't go anywhere else.

358
00:29:18,190 --> 00:29:20,230
This time, come back with me.

359
00:29:20,560 --> 00:29:22,160
Put everything aside for now

360
00:29:22,280 --> 00:29:23,890
