406
00:31:29,470 --> 00:31:30,670
He drove me here.

407
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:32,310
What?

408
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:34,280
He brought you here?

409
00:31:35,190 --> 00:31:36,430
Your father promised me

410
