412
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:39,630
Why?

413
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,410
Why can't we see each other?

414
00:31:43,430 --> 00:31:45,190
Mu, you're grown up now.

415
00:31:45,490 --> 00:31:46,560
