would be difficult to discipline.

438
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:27,630
Bold as brass,

439
00:32:27,840 --> 00:32:30,040
he's bound to get into trouble someday.

440
00:32:32,710 --> 00:32:33,310
Back then,

441
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:35,230
he called our home repeatedly.

442
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,960
I had warned him already.

443
00:32:37,670 --> 00:32:39,600
I didn't want you two associating.

444
00:32:43,840 --> 00:32:45,300
How could you understand?

445
00:32:46,840 --> 00:32:48,320
If you understood,

446
00:32:48,710 --> 00:32:49,710
you wouldn't have stayed away

447
00:32:49,710 --> 00:32:51,970
